@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zohqsp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(0.80))
    v2 = (v2 - (v1 - (v2 + 0.21 * tmp + 0.81)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(v0) * wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.29)))
    v0 = 0.94
    v0 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.16 * v1 + 0.65)) + wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.51)))
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.56) * v0)
    data[tid] = v0
